org.opentosca.toscana.plugins.cloudformation.visitor

Class CheckModelRelationshipVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opentosca.toscana.plugins.cloudformation.visitor.CloudFormationVisitor
      • org.opentosca.toscana.plugins.cloudformation.visitor.CheckModelRelationshipVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RelationshipVisitor, StrictRelationshipVisitor

    public class CheckModelRelationshipVisitor
extends CloudFormationVisitor
implements StrictRelationshipVisitor
    Checks the model's relationships whether they are supported or not.
    The visitor implements the StrictRelationshipVisitor interface which means every method that is not overridden will throw an UnsupportedTypeException. These types are not supported.
